## 💡 Quick Wins (Can Build in < 1 Day Each)

These are small but noticeable improvements:

1. **"Duplicate Trip" button** on My Trips page — clone an itinerary instantly
2. **Trip notes/comments** — free-text notes on each saved trip
3. **Custom PDF filename** — let agents set the filename (e.g., "Sharma_Family_Bali_March2026.pdf")
4. **Print-friendly view** — a clean browser print layout as an alternative to PDF
5. **Favorite/star trips** — pin frequently-used itineraries
6. **Search & filter** on My Trips — by destination, date range, client name
7. **"Copy itinerary as text"** — one-click copy to clipboard for pasting into WhatsApp/email

---

> **Bottom line:** The two features that will give you the biggest leap are **Inline Editing** and **Hotel/Flight Info**. Together, they transform the output from "AI draft" to "client-ready document" — which is exactly the promise that will get travel agents to pay for and stick with the tool.
